\id 2TI Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular 
\mt1 ﾆ、TAKURU PUULUSA ﾆ蟹MMURU HAA E TIMOTEE 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, mo Alla hoddiri wonugol *sahaabaajo Iisaa Almasiihu on, e telen-ma fodaari ngurndan wonﾉ預n e Iisaa Almasiihu on ﾉ預n. 
\p  
\v 2 Mi salminii maa yo Timotee, an oo boobo an mo mi yiﾉ擁 fota. Yo Alla Baabaajo on e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on yeﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴere e yurmeende e ﾉ砥ttu. 
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Wakkiliniri Timotee 
\p  
\v 3 Mi yettii Alla, on mo mi woni rewude, wano baabiraaﾉ兎 an ﾉ兎n non, e dow ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde, e hoore mi alaa yejjitude fii maa e nder torndeeji an ﾉ擁n jemma e ﾉｲalorma.  
\v 4 Ko fii miﾉ熔 andita fii gonﾉ擁 maa ﾉ擁n, awa miﾉ熔 faalaa yi'itude ma fota fii no mi heewira weltaare.  
\v 5 Miﾉ熔 andita kadi gomﾉ擁nal wongal e maa ngal, ngal aldaa e faasiqankaaku, wonnoongal e pati maa Lowiisi e yumma maa Eniisi, wano mi fellitiri non hingal e maa.  
\v 6 Ko ﾉ蓉n waﾉ擁 si mi wakkilinii ma huﾉ橡妬tugol ngal dokkal Alla, ngal hendornoﾉ預a *fawugol juuﾉ容 an ﾉ容n e hoore maa.  
\v 7 Ko fii ruuhu mo Alla yeﾉ擁 en on wonaa waﾉ熔owo en huluﾉ兎, kono ko ruuhu okkoowo en doole e giggol e waawugol hoore mun. 
\p  
\v 8 Awa wota a hersir seeditanagol Joomi men on, e min sokiraaﾉ熔 sabu makko on, kono tampidu e an fii Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo on e dow bawgal Alla,  
\v 9 on Danduﾉ熔 en, noddi en fii no naﾉ妬ren ngurndan men ﾉ預n no laaﾉ妬ri, hara hinaa sabu kuuﾉ容 men ﾉ容n, kono ko sabu haajaande makko nden tigi e moﾆｴﾆｴere nde yeﾉ擁raﾉ容n sabu Iisaa Almasiihu on nden, ado saa'iiji poomayankeeji ﾉ擁n.  
\v 10 Nden moﾆｴﾆｴere ﾉ殿nginiraama jooni feeﾉｲugol Iisaa Almasiihu, Danduﾉ熔 en on, on muncuﾉ熔 doole mayde nden. Ko Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo on o feﾉｲﾉｲinirani en ngurndan ﾉ預n lannataa ﾉ預n.  
\v 11 Ko fii oo Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo mi waﾉ擁raa waajotooﾉ熔 e sahaabaajo e jannoowo.  
\v 12 Ko sabu ﾉ蓉n mi heﾉ妬ri ﾉ擁i satteendeeji. Kono mi hersaa, ko fii miﾉ熔 andi ko hombo mi gomﾉ擁ni, awa miﾉ熔 felliti himo mari bawgal hiwugol ko mi halfinaa kon haa e ﾉｲalaande ﾉｲaawoore nden. 
\p  
\v 13 Awa jogito sifa ﾉ擁i konguﾉ擁 selluﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 hendorﾉ預a mi, e nder gomﾉ擁nal ngal e giggol wongol ngol e Iisaa Almasiihu on.  
\v 14 Jogitoﾉ預a kaliifu moﾆｴﾆｴo mo hendorﾉ預a *Ruuhu Seniiﾉ熔 on, ﾉ蓉n ko Wonﾉ熔 e men on. 
\p  
\v 15 Hiﾉ預 andi wonﾉ兎 leydi *Aazii ﾉ兎n fow tertike lan. Figeeli e Hermogaana no tawaa e ﾉ兎n.  
\v 16 Yo Joomiraaﾉ熔 on tippin yurmeende mun nden e hoore ﾉ兎ynguure Onesifoora nden, ko fii himo muﾉｲﾉｲinaynoo lan soono woo, awa kadi o hersiraano ko mi sokaa kon.  
\v 17 E hoore ﾉ蓉n, ﾉ殿y o arii Roomu, o catino e ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬tugol lan haa o yi'immi.  
\v 18 Yo Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yeﾉ熔y mo yurmeende mun nden ﾉｲande ﾉｲaawoore nden. Hiﾉ預 andi ﾉ砥ri wonﾉ熔 woo haa honto o wallimmi ko mi woni Efeesi. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 An kadi non, yo boobo an, tiiﾉ擁nor e moﾆｴﾆｴere wonde e Iisaa Almasiihu on nden.  
\v 2 Ko nanirﾉ預a mi kon e tawnde seedeeﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ兎, halfin ﾉ蓉n yimﾉ兎 holniiﾉ兎, waawayﾉ兎 kaﾉｲun kadi jannude woﾉ橡兎 goo.  
\v 3 Tampidu e an wa suufaajo moﾆｴﾆｴo Iisaa Almasiihu on.  
\v 4 Ko fii si suufaajo golloowo golle mun no faalaa weltinde hooreejo mun on, o hilnotaako haajuuji goo.  
\v 5 Ko fii foolotirteeﾉ熔 e dogudu waﾉ預ntaake *meetelol si o waﾉ擁raali no haaniri non.  
\v 6 Ko remoowo wakkiliiﾉ熔 on haani adaade hendaade geﾉ殿l mun ngal ka baagol.  
\v 7 Hakkilan koo ko mi woni wi'ude, ko fii Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yeﾉ容te faamu e ﾉ擁 fow. 
\p  
\v 8 Anditii fii Iisaa Almasiihu, on immitiiﾉ熔 e hakkunde mayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, iwruﾉ熔 e bolondaa Daawuuda on, wano Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo mo mi woni yottinde on wi'iri non,  
\v 9 on mo mi tampani haa mi haﾉ橡妬raa wa waﾉ熔owo bone. Kono daaluyee Alla on haﾉ橡殿aka.  
\v 10 Ko ﾉ蓉n waﾉ擁 si miﾉ熔 wakkilii fow sabu suﾉ殿aﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, fii kamﾉ兎 kadi no ﾉ兎 heﾉ妬ra kisiyee wonﾉ熔 e Iisaa Almasiihu on, wondude e darja poomayankeejo on.  
\v 11 Ngol kongol ko haqiiqawol wonde: 
\q1 Si en maayidii e makko, 
\q2 en wuuritidoyay kadi e makko. 
\q1  
\v 12 Si en ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲike, 
\q2 en laamodoyay kadi e makko. 
\q1 Si en yeddii kadi fii makko, 
\q2 kanko kadi o yeddoyay fii men. 
\q1  
\v 13 Si tawii en sellaa-finde, 
\q1 kanko ko o sella-findeejo, 
\q2 ko fii o waawataa yedditaade. 
\s1 Fii Golle Moﾆｴﾆｴe 
\p  
\v 14 E hino ko haanuﾉ預a andintinde kon: jeejaa yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yeeso Alla wonde, yo ﾉ兎 accu pooﾉ熔tiro haala ka aldaa e nafa. Si hinaa ﾉ蓉n, ﾉ蓉n nawray heﾉ熔tooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e majjere.  
\v 15 Eto no weeﾉ妬toraa yeeso Alla wa neﾉ遼熔 haanaaﾉ熔 jaﾉ兎ede, ﾉ蓉n ko golloowo mo hersaa, e tindinoowo daaluyee goongaajo on no feewiri.  
\v 16 Reenoﾉ預a e haalaaji mehi ﾉ擁 yaadaa e faale Alla on, ko fii jokkuﾉ兎 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎n ﾉ砥rtay tun woﾉ遼擁taade Alla.  
\v 17 Ko fii konguﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n no layira wa nawnaare ﾂｫmasara.ﾂｻ Himenee e Fileeti no tawaa e ﾉ兎n,  
\v 18 ﾉ兎n seluﾉ兎 goonga on, no bonnira gomﾉ擁nal woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n wi'ugol wonde ummutal ngal waﾉ擁ino.  
\v 19 E hin-le hayre didol tiiﾉ蓉nde nde Alla waﾉ擁 nden no ﾉｲiiﾉ妬 haa jooni, hinde notiraa ﾉ擁i konguﾉ擁 ﾉ熔o: ﾂｫJoomiraaﾉ熔 on no andi ﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n!ﾂｻ, awa kadi: ﾂｫKala jantiiﾉ熔 innde Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yo yilto e angal peewal.ﾂｻ\f a \fr 2:19 \ft 2.19 Ada. 16.5 \f* 
\p  
\v 20 E nder suudu hittundu hinaa miranji tafiraaﾉ擁 kaﾅ暁菊 maa kaalisi tun woni ton, kono kunnaaje e payanﾉ容 leydi kadi no ton. Miranji arani ﾉ擁n ko mariraaﾉ擁 fii haaju hittuﾉ熔, kono ﾉ擁ya ko huutorteeﾉ擁 fii ko woni woo.  
\v 21 On laﾉ橡妬nﾉ熔 hoore mun e ﾉ擁i piiji bonﾉ擁, o wonay miran hittuﾉ熔, huutorteeﾉ熔, laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔, mo jom mun huutorta, hebulaniiﾉ熔 kala kuugal moﾆｴﾆｴal. 
\p  
\v 22 Awa dogu himmeeji cukankaaku ﾉ擁n, ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿a peewal ngal e gomﾉ擁nal ngal e giggol ngol e ﾉ砥ttu on, wondude e jantorayﾉ兎 Joomiraaﾉ熔 on ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde.  
\v 23 Bugitoﾉ預a yeddondire njofooje ﾉ容 aldaa e nafa ﾉ容n, ﾉ容 anduﾉ預a adday hawreeji ﾉ容n.  
\v 24 Ko fii haanaa ka kurkantooﾉ熔 Joomiraaﾉ熔 on haﾉ妬dee. Himo haani wonde newaniiﾉ熔 fow, muﾉｲﾉｲiiﾉ熔, o waawa jannude.  
\v 25 Himo haani kadi wurtirde liddotooﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n no newori, e nder tanﾆｴinagol wonde Alla okkay ﾉ兎 feere no ﾉ兎 tuubira, ﾉ兎 anda goonga on,  
\v 26 ﾉ兎 ruttoo e faamu maﾉ橡兎 moﾆｴﾆｴo on, e no ﾉ兎 sortora e pircol Ibuliisa nanguﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 fii waﾉ蓉gol faale mun on. 
\c 3  
\s1 Fii Sakkitoode Aduna on 
\p  
\v 1 Awa andu wonde ka sakkitoode aduna, sattoyay fota.  
\v 2 Ko fii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n laatoyto ﾉ砥rtintiniiﾉ兎, yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 kaalisi, mantiiﾉ兎, hownitiiﾉ兎, hoynooﾉ兎, dartotooﾉ兎 mawﾉ兎 mun, dulluﾉ兎, hayfinooﾉ兎 fii laawol feewungol ngol,  
\v 3 ﾉ兎 yurmetaake, ﾉ兎 rippotaako, aybinooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 waawataa hoore mun, hunﾆｴuﾉ兎, ayﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴere,  
\v 4 janfotooﾉ兎, huuwirooﾉ兎 angal faamu, heewuﾉ兎 townitaare, yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 faale mun on ﾉ砥ri Alla.  
\v 5 Hara hiﾉ兎 ﾉ殿ngini e kene dewal ngal, kono hara hiﾉ兎 yeddi ko ngal wondi e bawgal kon. Awa pottito ﾉ兎n yimﾉ兎 ﾉ熔n. 
\p  
\v 6 No woodi e maﾉ橡兎 naatooﾉ兎 ka cuuﾉ擁, pooﾉ預 rewﾉ兎 lo'uﾉ兎 fawiiﾉ兎 junuubi, ﾉ兎 kala noone himmeeji ardii.  
\v 7 ﾆ‘n rewﾉ兎 no janga ﾉｲande woo, kono hara ﾉ兎 waawataa andude goonga on few.  
\v 8 Ko wano Janeesi e Jambereesi dartornoo Muusaa non, ko wano non ﾉ兎n yimﾉ兎 kadi dartorta goonga on. ﾆ‘n ko yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 hakkille mun bonnaa, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nal mun wonaa haqiiqawal.  
\v 9 Kono ﾉ兎 yaarataa yeeso, ko fii feetere maﾉ橡兎 nden ﾉ殿nganay fow, wano no ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 wowlaaﾉ兎 fii mun non. 
\s1 Fii no Timotee Wakkiliniraa e ko Jannaa kon 
\p  
\v 10 Kono an, a catike fota e janndeeji an ﾉ擁n e jikkuuji an ﾉ擁n e anniyeeji an ﾉ擁n e gomﾉ擁nal an ngal e muﾉｲal an ngal e giggol an ngol e ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲaare an nden.  
\v 11 Hiﾉ預 andi kadi ko mi jokkaa kon e tampereeji an ﾉ擁 mi heﾉ妬 e ﾉ容e ca'e Antiyoosi-Pisidii, Ikoniim e Listaara ﾉ擁n, e cukkanﾉ容 ﾉ容 mi heﾉ妬 ﾉ容n e no Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yaltinirimmi e ﾉ蓉n fow.  
\v 12 ﾆ隔n-le wuren, kala faalaaﾉ兎 wuurude e hoore dewal e nder humondiral e Iisaa Almasiihu on ﾉ兎n fow cukkete.  
\v 13 Kono yimﾉ兎 bonﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e ﾆｴoﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n soono woo ﾉ砥rtay tun yaarude e nder bone on, ﾉ兎 ﾉ預yna hoore maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ynora heddiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi.  
\v 14 Kono an, cato e ko janguﾉ預a kon, ﾉ蓉n ko ko hendorﾉ預a hoolaare, hiﾉ預 andi ko hombo heﾉ妬rﾉ預a ﾉ蓉n.  
\v 15 Gila e paykunyaagal maa hiﾉ預 andi bindi seniiﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n. Hiﾉ擁 waawu-maa okkude faamu fii kisiyee on sabu gomﾉ擁ngol Iisaa Almasiihu on.  
\v 16 Kala daalol windiingol ko foofaango Alla, hingol wondi e nafa fii jannugol e hollugol ellaaji e wurtugol e ne'ugol e nder peewal,  
\v 17 fii no aaden Alla on eltiree, hebulanoo waﾉ蓉gol kala kuugal moﾆｴﾆｴal. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Ko ﾉ蓉n waﾉ擁, e yeeso Alla e Iisaa Almasiihu on, on ﾉｲaawayﾉ熔 wurﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e mayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, e sabu ardu makko ndun e *laamu makko ngun, mi yamirii ma, mi tentinii:  
\v 2 waajo fii daaluyee on, catoﾉ預a e ﾉ蓉n, nde heﾉ砥ﾉ預a fajuhun weeﾉ砥kun woo, maa a heﾉ殿a, hollaa ﾉ兎 ellaaji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, felaa ﾉ兎, wakkilinaa ﾉ兎 e hoore jannugol e nder muﾉｲal timmungal.  
\v 3 Ko fii saa'i no aroya nde tawata yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n jaﾉ殿taa hande kadi jannde sellunde nden, kono tippude e faaleeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿nnay takko maﾉ橡兎 karamokooﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ko yewta ﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 faalaa nanude kon.  
\v 4 ﾆ‘ udda noppi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e goonga on, ﾉ兎 fewta tindi mehi ﾉ擁n.  
\v 5 Kono an non, wonu hakkilanﾉ熔 e ﾉ擁 fow, wakkiloﾉ預a tampereeji ﾉ擁n, waﾉ預a kuuﾉ容 waajotooﾉ熔 fii Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo on, timminiraa golle maa ﾉ容n no feewiri. 
\p  
\v 6 Ko fii min, miﾉ熔 itti wonkii an kin wa sadaka hibbaaﾉ熔 fii Alla, ko fii saa'i fokkitugol an ngol hewtii.  
\v 7 Mi tippirii tippiro moﾆｴﾆｴo ngon, mi timminii dogudu an ndun, mi woni sella-findeejo e telen-ma gomﾉ擁nal ngal.  
\v 8 Jooni non miﾉ熔 maranaa *meetelol peewal ngol. Joomi on, on ﾆ拌awoowo Feewuﾉ熔, jonnoyay lan ngol ka ﾉｲalaande sakkitorde, ﾉ蓉n non hinaa min tun, kono ko kala himmanﾉ熔 feeﾉｲitugol makko ngol kadi. 
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Waajori Timotee 
\p  
\v 9 Awa eto araa, tawaa mi ko ﾉ砥ri yaawude.  
\v 10 Ko fii Demaasi tertike lan, sabu yiﾉ蓉gol mo oo aduna fewndiiﾉ熔. O yahii Tesalonii. Kiriskiisu kadi yahii Galaasi, Tiituusa kadi yahii Dalamaasi.  
\v 11 Ko min tun e Luuka wondi. Ardu e Markuusa, ko fii himo hitti e an fota fii golle ﾉ容n.  
\v 12 Mi imminii Tikiiki Efeesi.  
\v 13 Nde hiﾉ預 ara, addoraa burmusu mo mi acciri Karpuusi on ka wi'etee ﾉ熔n Turuwaasi, e defte ﾉ容n, tentinii guri windeteeﾉ擁 e mun ﾉ擁n.  
\v 14 Oo siyaakeejo wi'eteeﾉ熔 Aleksander waﾉ擁i lan boneeji buy, kono Joomiraaﾉ熔 on jonnitay mo ittiri kuuﾉ容 makko ﾉ容n.  
\v 15 An kadi reeno e makko, ko fii o dartike konguﾉ擁 men ﾉ擁n no tiiﾉ擁ri. 
\p  
\v 16 Ko mi adii dandude hoore an ka ﾉｲaawirdu, hay gooto wallitanooki lan, kono fow tertino lan. Wota ﾉ蓉n jogitane ﾉ兎.  
\v 17 Ko Joomiraaﾉ熔 on wallitinoo lan, tiiﾉ擁nimmi, fii no mi timminira yottingol Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo on, e fii no leﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n fow nanira ﾉ蓉n. Awa kadi mi jattinaa hunduko ngayuuri ndin.  
\v 18 Ko Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yaltintammi e kala kuugal bongal, o dandammi fii no o naadirammi ka nder laamateeri makko kammuyankeeri. Yo mangural wonan mo haa poomaa. Aamiina! 
\s1 Fii Salminaango ngon 
\p  
\v 19 Mi salminii Piriskiila e Akiila, e ﾉ兎ynguure Onesifoora nden.  
\v 20 Awa Arastuusa kaﾉｲun no Korenti. Mi accu kadi Torofiimi no nawni ka saare Miletii.  
\v 21 Eto araa ado ndungude. Ebuluusu e Pudeniisi e Linuusa e Kaludiiyata, wondude e musiﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n fow salminii ma. 
\p  
\v 22 Yo Joomiraaﾉ熔 on wondu e maa, awa kadi yo moﾆｴﾆｴere makko nden wonu e mon.